<li><b>Week Seven</b>
  <ul>
    <li><i>Monday 13 February</i>: No reading. In class we will cover
    Julia Sets for complex functions and the chaos game. 
    <li><i>Thursday 16 February</i>: Read Images of Chaos, from
    Gleick. Bring a Julia set to class.  In class we'll discuss the
    Mandelbrot set. 
    <li><b><a href="./homework.7.html">Homework 7</a></b>, due Friday,
    February 23. 
  
  </ul>

